t-size: xx-large;\"><strong>40歲</strong>重扮青春</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:21:18.000Z","msg":"中聯辦嘅簡人方向都係咁<br />\n可能佢地研究過係香港尤其班老野好buy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e42ae34f8f18e1a9d3ce2f959223f2d015ba88","tid":787782,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571feda33a9bb9748d2385cedc8ebcb346caab39","tid":787782,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"廣告有雷凱欣就話望吓姐<br />\n你陳凱欣邊位呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"前TVB及now記者及主播，後生未必識佢。<br />\n專做醫療新聞，伊拉克戰爭時同譚衛兒及黃應士去過科威特。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃應士帶防毒面具，譚衛兒同佢用毛巾掩住口鼻。<br />\n仲有有D宮心計嘅嘢要問吓李燦榮啦～"}]}